vrptw.algorithm.subproblem.labelalgorithm

类 EspptwccViaLabelCorrecting

  • java.lang.Object
    • vrptw.algorithm.subproblem.AbstractPriceProblem
      • vrptw.algorithm.subproblem.labelalgorithm.EspptwccViaLabelCorrecting
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    LabelAlgorithm

    public class EspptwccViaLabelCorrecting
extends AbstractPriceProblem
implements LabelAlgorithm
    Solve an ESPPTWCC via dynamic programming labeling approach
    see "3.4. Description of the Algorithm"in Feillet et al. (2006):
    An Exact Algorithm for the Elementary Shortest Path Problem with Resource Constraints:
    Application to Some Vehicle Routing Problems.
    从以下版本开始:
    JDK1.8
    版本:
    V1.0
    作者:
    Xiong Wangqi

      private class  EspptwccViaLabelCorrecting.EsppcctwLabel
      ESPPTWCC 专用 Label，增加两类资源：
      1 访问过的节点的数量
      2 visitation vector，已经访问过的点为 1，未访问的为 0.
